379
00:24:17,918 --> 00:24:19,128
Apa itu benar?

380
00:24:26,051 --> 00:24:27,469
Menurutmu begitu?

381
00:24:33,559 --> 00:24:35,811
Hanya pukulan pertama yang termasuk

382
00:24:35,894 --> 00:24:37,479
